### Adding a new weather
POST http://localhost:3000/weather
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "date": "2025-10-20", 
    "mintemp":10,
    "temp": 25, 
    "weather": "Zivatar",
    "userid": 2
}

###Getting a new weather
GET http://localhost:3000/weather
Content-Type: application/json

### adat törtlés id alapján
DELETE  http://localhost:3000/weather/1
Content-Type: application/json

### Időjárás kiírása user id-vel
GET http://localhost:3000/weather/user/1
